{"talk":{"id":71487,"name":"Elaine Fong: My mother's final wish -- and the right to die with dignity","description":"After a terminal cancer diagnosis upended 12 years of remission, all Elaine Fong's mother wanted was a peaceful end of life. What she received instead became a fight for the right to decide when. Fong shares the heart-rending journey to honor her mother's choice for a death with dignity -- and reflects on the need to explore our relationship to dying so that we may redesign this final and most universal of human experiences.","slug":"elaine_fong_my_mother_s_final_wish_and_the_right_to_die_with_dignity","recorded_at":"2017-10-10 00:00:00","published_at":"2021-03-03 16:00:23","updated_at":"2021-11-03 09:09:27","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":522,"name":"TEDxSanFrancisco"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/159de27ed34ef6879701ebf356a79aa53f6d1be6_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/159de27ed34ef6879701ebf356a79aa53f6d1be6_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/159de27ed34ef6879701ebf356a79aa53f6d1be6_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/159de27ed34ef6879701ebf356a79aa53f6d1be6_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/dbf5899d93816e120d6e1785e2cd4e2af0cfbfe6_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/ElaineFong_2017X-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":10550377,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/ElaineFong_2017X-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":29323141,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/ElaineFong_2017X-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":51836618,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"450